The Honey Baked Ham Company provides specialty ham and turkey for any occasion. The company started in Michigan over 40 years ago and now have over 400 stores throughout the United States.

This dataset displays all of the Honey Baked Ham Company Store locations across the United States. The dataset contains the store's full physical address, phone, and lat/lon coordinates. Addresses were obtained from borders.com and are current as of 12.2007. Addresses were geocoded to obtain their lat/lon coordinates.
